	<!--==========================
	Services Section
	============================-->
	<section id="services">
		<div class="container wow fadeInUp">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12">
					<h3 class="section-title">DERTRIX</h3>
					<div class="section-title-divider"></div>
					<p class="section-description">Learning outcome management and analysis to promote student success. </p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">

				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-road"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Proactive Communication Tools</a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">
						Dertrix puts powerful tools into a highly intuitive system and ensures everyone is communicating using the same platform.
						From school news to scheduling a meeting, responding to important school news or posts, Dertrix makes things easy, secure and transparent.
						
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Connecting Everyone</a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">
						The Dertrix (user) experience has been designed to bring staff and parents together.
						Parents and guardians can explore and interact with the school members of staff, access their child/ren’s grades and reports, view and upload documents within the school portal.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Intelligent Grade Calculation </a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">
						Take the hassle out of grade management using our intelligent grade processing tool. 
						The feature automatically work out students’ grades  as soon as results are updated. 
						The grade management tool offers a full audit control so no changes are done without records being logged.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-photo"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Simple and Effective Event Management</a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">
						Our management dashboard allows you to create, manage and share events with parents and guardians. 
						Keep an eye on planned or upcoming events. 
						This feature helps increase engagement and encourage participant communication at all stages of the event – before, during, and after.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-bar-chart"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Report Analysis </a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">
						Dertrix empowers management with vital reports such as academic performance, user engagement and many more, 
						giving management reliable data which can be used in the planning and decision making process. 
						Reports can be viewed and downloaded easily, saving time and improving efficiency.
					</p>
				</div>



				<div class="col-md-4 service-item">
					<div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-shopping-bag"></i></div>
					<h4 class="service-title"><a href="">Cloud-based platform </a></h4>
					<p class="service-description">Fully cloud-based and mobile-ready, parents and guardians can access your school portal anywhere,
					at any time, via any devices of their choice, in any corner of the world as long as they are  connected to the internet,
					helping you unlock the full value and identity of your school.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
